Data provenance
================================================================================
The curated dependency graph in data/*.json is a HAND-CURATED compilation assembled from public sources
(Wikidata, SEC EDGAR, company filings and investor materials), 2025-2026. It is NOT derived from Diffbot or any
proprietary knowledge graph. The individual facts are public; the curated *compilation* is the copyrightable work
licensed here under CC-BY-4.0 — reuse with attribution to "Jose Luis Latorre Millas / MarketMind".

================================================================================
What is intentionally NOT in this repository
================================================================================
- Market-price / abnormal-return data derived from Yahoo Finance (via yfinance) is NOT distributed here
  (Yahoo Terms of Service prohibit redistribution). The builder script (tools/build_golden_dataset.py) is
  included so anyone can regenerate that dataset locally from a price source of their choosing; its output is not.
- Any live-news ingestion, trading strategy, position sizing, or P&L-tuned weights. This repository is the
  reasoning SUBSTRATE (graph + engine + honest validation harness), not a trading system.

